      "target": {
        "kind": "pull_request",
        "title": "fix(heartbeat): remove static iteration cap in seekNextActivePhaseDueMs",
        "body": "## What Problem This Solves\n\nFixes an issue where agents configured with sub-minute heartbeat intervals\n(\\`every: 30s\\`, \\`every: 10s\\`, etc.) and active hours windows would\npermanently stop running heartbeats when the current time fell outside the\nactive window.\n\nRoot cause: \\`seekNextActivePhaseDueMs\\` had a static iteration cap of\n10,080 (calibrated for 1-minute intervals). When \\`intervalMs < 60_000\\`,\nthe cap was reached before the 7-day time horizon, returning \\`startMs\\`\n— outside active hours — and heartbeats stuck in a busy-loop.\n\n## Why This Change Was Made\n\nTwo-tier seek strategy that stays bounded for all intervals while never\nskipping phase-aligned candidates inside active windows:\n\n- **intervalMs >= 1s**: per-candidate scan — naturally bounded by the\n  7-day horizon (max 604,800 iterations for 1s, 10,080 for 60s+)\n- **intervalMs < 1s**: batch in whole-interval multiples >= 1s, with a\n  **backward walk** on inactive->active transitions to find the earliest\n  phase-aligned slot. Batch keeps prediate calls <= 604,800 regardless\n  of intervalMs.\n\n## User Impact\n\nUsers with sub-minute heartbeat intervals and active hours can now\ncorrectly seek into the next active window. Sub-second intervals are\nbatched to keep the production \\`isWithinActiveHours\\` predicate cost\nbounded. No impact on minute-or-larger intervals.\n\n## Evidence\n\n**Unit tests (19/19 pass):** 14 existing + 5 new\n- 30s interval / 09:00-17:00: finds 09:00 next day, phase-aligned\n- 59s interval / 1min narrow window (09:00-09:01): finds 09:00:43 (977 steps)\n- 500ms interval, startMs active: returns startMs directly (no backward walk)\n- 500ms interval, inactive->active transition: backward walk finds 09:00:00.000\n- 1ms interval / never-active: bounded at 604,800 iterations, sub-50ms\n\n**Real behavior proof (6 scenarios via \\`node --import tsx\\`):**\n\\`\\`\\`\n=== seekNextActivePhaseDueMs v5 (two-tier, 604k max iter) ===\n\n1. 30s, 09:00-17:00, start 17:00 -> 2026-01-02 09:00:00 UTC (active: true)\n2. 59s, 09:00-09:01 window, start 17:00 -> 2026-01-02 09:00:43 UTC (steps: 977)\n3. 7s, always-active, start 12:00 -> 12:00 (startMs: true)\n4. 1s, never-active, start 12:00 -> 12:00 (elapsed: 3.2ms)\n5. computeNextHeartbeatPhaseDueMs (30s), now 10:00 -> 10:00:30\n6. Full-path: 30s, 20:00->09-17 active -> 2026-06-26 09:00:15 UTC\n\nAll 6 scenarios passed.\n\\`\\`\\`\n",
        "branch": "fix/heartbeat-remove-static-iteration-cap",
